{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM02_130.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x19,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x4f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "That should do it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "...I'm able to make a lot of things now. Your pages are filling up little by little, Plachta."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Thanks to you, I've regained another memory."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Really!? What kind of memory is it this time?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Apparently, I used to be an alchemist."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Huh... So that's why you know so much about alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "But that's pretty amazing. You're a book, yet you were also an alchemist!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "No, it seems I wasn't always a book. I was a human before I took this form."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Wait... WHAAAAAAAAT!? Y-you're kidding me!? You were... Human before!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "U-um... Then um, why did you become a book?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Did you really like books, so much that you wanted to become one? Or did you mess something up while using alchemy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "...I'm sorry. Unfortunately, I still can't remember anything about that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "However... It seems I placed my soul within a book to accomplish something very important..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Something important... But I guess we can't do anything about it if you don't remember..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "...Hey Plachta, I just thought of something. You said you were human before, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Then maybe, just maybe. Maybe if you were able to turn back into a human..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Then all of your memories would come back at once! Although I'm not sure about that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "...If it was possible to return to human form, I don't think that would be too far-fetched."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Really? Alright! In that case, let's..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "No, I believe it would require extremely advanced alchemic techniques. I doubt you could perform that as you are now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Uu, you're right. I don't even have the slightest idea what I'd need to do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I'm thankful that you're thinking about me, but its feasibility seems low."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Uu, I thought it was a good idea..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Plachta told you about a new gathering field that she remembered."
        }
    ]
}